stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> PowerOff

    PowerOff --> Startup: power switch on

    Startup --> Initialising: begin setup

    Initialising --> Ready: camera and SD card ready
    Initialising --> Error: initialisation failed

    Ready --> Capturing: shutter button pressed
    Ready --> GalleryMode: gallery mode selected
    Ready --> SettingsMode: mode button pressed
    Ready --> LowBattery: battery below threshold
    Ready --> PowerOff: power switch off

    Capturing --> Saving: image captured successfully
    Capturing --> Error: camera capture failed

    Saving --> PhotoSaved: JPEG written to microSD
    Saving --> Error: SD write failed
